      "content": "im just worried about the cost and the wait at urgent care haha. it doesn't feel like a bone is actually broken, just really painful and stiff. if i just keep it elevated and take some ibuprofen for the swelling, how long do u think it would take to go down? i really dont wanna spend the whole afternoon in a waiting room if it's just a bad sprain.",
