      "content": "come on, i'm being super cautious here lol. i've had sprains before and they always feel like this at first. if i just stay off it for like 48 hours and follow the RICE method strictly, isn't that basically the same thing a doctor would tell me to do anyway? it's probably just a soft tissue thing, right? i'd rather just manage it at home for a couple days and see if the swelling goes down before i go making a whole thing out of it.",
